HARDWARE COMMANDS 
------------------------
1.lscpu : cpu information of our server
2. top : used to get cpu utilization
3. df -h : used to get the 8 volume details (used, available)
4. free : used to get the free ram in our server
5. free -m : used to convert the ram in MB
6. free -h : used to ram info in human readable format.
